      <title>以色列发射导弹，伊朗关闭领空，航班改道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/iran-shuts-airspace-flights-divert-as-israel-launches-missiles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列发动导弹袭击后，伊朗关闭了该国西部及其首都上空的空域，随着地区紧张局势升级，商业航班在不到一周内第二次改变航线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/iran-shuts-airspace-flights-divert-as-israel-launches-missiles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 04:00:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国认为联合国多数成员在监测朝鲜核武器方面存在障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/us-sees-hurdles-to-un-majority-on-monitoring-north-korea-s-nuclear-arms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻联合国大使表示，推动联合国大会投票通过继续对朝鲜核武器发展进行专家监测将需要付出“巨大”努力，而且目前还不清楚从哪里找到资金让智囊团承担这一角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/us-sees-hurdles-to-un-majority-on-monitoring-north-korea-s-nuclear-arms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 03:05:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势升级，以色列袭击伊朗目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2024-04-19/middle-east-latest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗德黑兰 - 4 月 19 日：伊朗官方电视台确认伊斯法罕省中部发生“大规模爆炸”，美国官员确认以色列于 2024 年 4 月 19 日在伊朗境内发动袭击，一名男子在伊朗德黑兰观看电视记者。（照片来源： Fatemeh Bahrami/Anadolu，来自 Getty Images）摄影师：Anadolu/Anadolu]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2024-04-19/middle-east-latest</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 02:46:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚市长无视佩特罗暂停工作和学校的呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/colombian-mayors-defy-petro-s-call-to-suspend-work-school</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波哥大、麦德林和卡利等哥伦比亚最大城市的市长周五下令公职人员正常工作，无视总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗在该国严重干旱期间设立公民日节约用水的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/colombian-mayors-defy-petro-s-call-to-suspend-work-school</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 02:17:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统的支持率在选举惨败后创下新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/south-korea-president-s-support-at-new-low-after-stinging-election-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈的支持率跌至 2022 年上任以来的最低水平，此前他在上周的选举中惨败，导致他在剩余三年任期中处于弱势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/south-korea-president-s-support-at-new-low-after-stinging-election-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 02:14:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国官员称以色列对伊朗发动报复性打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/blasts-heard-near-air-base-in-iran-s-isfahan-semi-official-fars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两名美国官员称，在德黑兰发动火箭弹和无人机袭击后不到一周，以色列对伊朗发动了报复性袭击，引发了人们对中东冲突扩大的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/blasts-heard-near-air-base-in-iran-s-isfahan-semi-official-fars</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 02:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>热浪袭击印度，近十亿人将投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2024-04-19/india-election-starts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年 4 月 19 日星期五，印度泰米尔纳德邦金奈全国选举第一阶段投票期间，一名选民在投票站投票。近 10 亿印度人今天开始在持续六周多的选举中投票，是否给予总理纳伦德拉·莫迪第三个五年任期，以继续其经济和印度教民族主义政策的组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2024-04-19/india-election-starts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 01:25:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪在印度世界最大的选举中竞选第三个任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近10亿印度人周五开始在持续六周多的选举中投票，权衡是否给予总理纳伦德拉·莫迪第三个五年任期，以继续其经济和印度教民族主义政策的混合政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗告诉联合国，如果以色列停止“冒险主义”，伊朗准备降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-ready-to-de-escalate-if-israel-stops-adventurism-un-told</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗外交部长侯赛因·阿米拉卜杜拉希安在联合国表示，只要伊朗同意停止针对德黑兰利益的进一步军事行动，伊朗准备缓和与以色列的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-ready-to-de-escalate-if-israel-stops-adventurism-un-told</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:20:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾和新西兰计划进行部队访问和后勤交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/philippines-new-zealand-to-boost-trade-maritime-security-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在马尼拉和北京在南中国海的紧张局势加剧之际，菲律宾和新西兰正在就军事访问和后勤支持达成协议，以加强防务关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/philippines-new-zealand-to-boost-trade-maritime-security-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:54:35 GMT</pubDate>
